## 1. Stack

| Layer | Technology | Version |
|---|---|---|
| Framework | SvelteKit | 2 |
| UI | Svelte 5 (runes) | 5 |
| Language | TypeScript (strict) | 5 |
| CSS | Tailwind CSS | v4 |
| Components | shadcn-svelte (bits-ui) | — |
| ORM | Prisma + `@prisma/adapter-pg` | v7 |
| Database | PostgreSQL (Vercel Postgres / Neon) | — |
