## 2. Architecture — Feature-Sliced Design (FSD)

```
src/
  pages/            # page-level components (home, lists, list-details, media-details, profile, layout, signin)
    <page>/
      <page>.svelte         # root component (thin, mostly composition)
      <page>.types.ts       # local types
      index.ts              # barrel export
      ui/                   # sub-components (extracted from the page)
  features/         # isolated features: theme-toggler, locale-selector
  widgets/          # composite blocks: app-sidebar
  shared/
    config/
      domain.ts     # ALL domain constants — WATCH_STATUSES, MEDIA_TYPES, MEDIA_TYPE_META,
                    #   WATCH_STATUS_META, PROVIDER_META, FREE_PROVIDERS, KEY_REQUIRED_PROVIDERS
    lib/
      labels.ts     # getMediaTypeMeta, getWatchStatusLabels, getVisibilityLabel, formatCountry
      html.ts       # sanitizeHtml (DOMPurify), stripHtml
      scroll-fade.ts # scrollFade Svelte action (scroll fade CSS mask)
    types/
      common.ts
  lib/
    server/
      providers/    # ProviderAdapter implementations: anilist, jikan, kitsu, omdb, tmdb, trakt, tvdb, types.ts
      repositories/ # list-items.repository.ts, lists.repository.ts, media.repository.ts, index.ts
      external.ts   # searchExternal, importExternalMedia (deduplication)
      crypto.ts     # encrypt / decrypt (AES-256-GCM)
      prisma.ts     # PrismaClient singleton
      env.ts        # typed env var access
      locale.ts     # server-side locale helpers
    components/ui/  # shadcn components: button, input, select, sidebar, sheet, breadcrumb, skeleton, tooltip, separator
    paraglide/      # auto-generated by Paraglide
  routes/           # SvelteKit routing (+page.svelte, +page.server.ts, api/**/+server.ts)
```

