## 9. External providers

```typescript
// src/lib/server/external.ts
import { searchExternal, importExternalMedia } from '$lib/server/external'

const userKeys = await loadUserKeys(session.user.id)
const results = await searchExternal(query, userKeys)
// Results are auto-deduplicated by `${normalizeTitle}|${year}|${mediaType}` key
```

Provider adapters: `src/lib/server/providers/{anilist,jikan,kitsu,tmdb,omdb,tvdb,trakt}.ts` — each implements `ProviderAdapter` from `types.ts`.

API key encryption: `src/lib/server/crypto.ts` — AES-256-GCM, key from `API_KEYS_ENCRYPTION_KEY` env var.

