## 10. i18n (Paraglide.js)

```svelte
import { L } from '$lib'

<!-- ✅ Always use L, never hardcode strings -->
<p>{L.home_all_genres()}</p>
{L.media_season_number({ n: season })}

<!-- ❌ Forbidden -->
<p>All genres</p>
```

- Supported locales: `en`, `ru`, `fr`, `ja`, `zh`
- Message files: `messages/{en,ru,fr,ja,zh}.json`
- **All 5 files must be updated simultaneously when adding a new key**
- Keys are `snake_case` prefixed with the page/domain: `home_`, `media_`, `profile_`, `common_`, `list_`, `lists_`
- Provider setup steps: keys like `profile_tmdb_step_1`, resolved dynamically in `profile.svelte`

