## 13. Mandatory workflow after ANY code change

```bash
# 1. Auto-fix ESLint (formatting, import order, etc.)
npx eslint --fix src/path/to/changed-file.svelte

# 2. Type check
npm run check
```

Never skip these. The project uses strict ESLint (`unicorn`, `sonarjs`, `prettier`, `import/order`) and `svelte-check` catches type errors invisible to plain `tsc`.

